ResonantChain.AttributesDescription: Resonance Skill DMG Bonus is increased by 30%.
Reset Resonance Skill's Cooldown when Rover enters the Dark Surge state by casting Heavy Attack Devastation.
In the Dark Surge state, Basic Attack 5 restores HP equal to 10% of total HP lost on hit.
Heavy Attack Devastation and Resonance Liberation Deadening Abyss reduces enemy's Havoc RES by 10% for 20s on hit.
In the Dark Surge state, Basic Attack 5 deals an additional Havoc DMG equal to 50% of Basic Attack 5 DMG.
In the Dark Surge state, Rover's Crit. Rate is increased by 25%.

Words.Title: Idle: II
Words.Content: This is a testament to my connection with the world around me, and it's very much my companion now, bearing witness to everything I've experienced on this journey.

Words.Title: Idle: III
Words.Content: It is natural to feel dreadful of the unknown, yet... there are times when the unknown harbors hope, like how I can never know what else this power has to offer.

Words.Title: Join Team: I
Words.Content: We still have a long journey ahead of us. Let's press on.

Words.Title: Join Team: III
Words.Content: I will be there for everyone... As we head toward our shared future, leaving the past behind.

Words.Title: Ascension: I
Words.Content: The world around me... I can hear it clearer now.

Words.Title: Ascension: II
Words.Content: This power... it's mysterious, yet reassuring nonetheless.

Words.Title: Ascension: III
Words.Content: I still need more time to acquaint myself with this unfamiliar world.

Words.Title: Ascension: IV
Words.Content: A new journey awaits? Brimming with novel sounds, stories, and... fragmented memories.

Words.Title: Ascension: V
Words.Content: The place where the land ends is where the ocean begins. Our journey is far from ending.
